headline: Walmart (WMT): Examining Valuation as Investor Interest Grows
summary: Walmart (WMT) has been catching investor attention lately, and for good reason. Anytime the world’s largest retailer makes moves, it naturally raises the question: are we looking at a lasting signal, or is this just a blip on the radar? There hasn’t been a specific event this week to drive headlines, but the stock’s continued steady performance could signal changing expectations about its growth outlook. Taking a step back, Walmart’s shares have posted solid gains over the past year, rising...

headline: Walmart CEO Issues Wake-Up Call: ‘AI Is Going to Change Literally Every Job’
summary: The country’s largest private employer says its head count will stay flat over the next three years, despite plans to grow, as AI eliminates some roles and transforms others.
